Titolo: A Fork in the Tale

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: A Fork in the Tale is a full motion video (FMV) comedic adventure game developed by Advance Reality Interactive and published  by Any River Entertainment on February 28, 1997. The game draws a heavy influence from Don Bluth's Dragon's Lair games and features Bay Area actors Dale Morris, Fred Smith, Michael Ronin Orlando, Eric Carlson, Kaliopi Eleni, Jett, Pamela Herron and Jody Mortara among the fifty plus roles, as well as voice-overs by comedian Rob Schneider. Because of the large number of video sequences, the game was originally released on 5 CDs.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
